<div class="section_title"> 2005 International CES Exhibitor Workshop: Free to Exhibitors!</div>
<span class="text">
Save the date, book your room, and register to attend this FREE workshop for 2005 International CES exhibitors!
<P>JUST ANNOUNCED: Listen and Learn From the Experts at the exhibitor panel with Jim Jardin of Directed Electronics, Jon Bromberg of Microsoft, Terry Shorrock of Panasonic, and Lou Ann Thomas of Philips.</P>
<P>Attend this free workshop on Tuesday, September 21, 2004, at the Las Vegas Convention Center, and you’ll walk away with vendor discounts, face time with International CES representatives and other exhibitors,&nbsp;and exclusive insight on how to make your exhibit a true success.</P>
<P><A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/workshop/default.asp">Register to attend and check out the agenda.</A></P>
