<div class="section_title">CES Unveiled: The Official Press Event of the International CES</div>
<span class="text">
<DIV><IMG height=54 src="/print/images/promotions/CESUnveiled.gif" width=275></DIV>
<P>We’re excited to announce CES Unveiled: The Official Press Event of the International CES, 4-7 p.m. Tuesday, January 4, 2005, conveniently located at the Las Vegas Convention Center, Room S226. </P>
<P>Only credentialed media and analysts can attend this exclusive CEA-sponsored event. This is the only on-site pre-show press event that gives press and financial/market analysts a preview of the Innovations Design and Engineering Showcase honorees, Best of Innovations and exhibitor displays. </P>Interested in reaching this important group? Contact Ryan Strowger, Manager, Business Development, CEA at <A href="mailto:rstrowger@CE.org">rstrowger@CE.org</A> or 703-907-7679.
</span>
