<div class="section_title">Innovations 2005 Design and Engineering Awards</div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=114 hspace=8 src="/print/images/general/innovations2k5_75x114.gif" width=75 align=right vspace=2>Are you a brilliant design pro slaving away? Or, are you napping, to recharge your creative juices? Either way, it’s time to get the recognition you deserve for the year’s most inspirational and innovative designs.
<P>You’re one of the few, the proud and incredibly talented. The <A href="/print/attendees/awards/innovations/default.asp">Innovations 2005 Design and Engineering Awards</A> honor superior design and engineering among the year's most technologically advanced products in a wide range of consumer electronics categories. </P>Whether you design the products, bring them to market or retail them, you’ve been toiling to bring them to a higher level.<BR><BR>Enter your designs in this prestigious awards program September 13 through October 4, 2004. &nbsp;Honorees will be announced at the <A href="/print/exhibitors/promotions/press.asp#660">New York International CES Press Preview</A>, attended by the industry’s most elite members of the media on November 10, 2004. <BR><BR>Check out the complete <A href="/print/attendees/awards/innovations/details.asp">program details</A>. Questions? Please <A href="mailto:innovations@ce.org">contact us</A>, or call (703) 907-7432. We look forward to receiving your entries!
</span>
